fields.physical_description:
[board games] Circular solitaire board of varnished wood mounted on three button feet, with hemispherical holes for thirty four marbles, linked by pigmented lines.  Nine of the holes are linked by a squared framework marked out in dark green.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a swirled yellow latticino core and alternating white and coloured stripes (a red, a green and a blue).
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a swirled yellow latticino core and alternating coloured stripes with white edges (two red, a green and a blue).
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a swirled white latticino core and alternating coloured stripes (three red, a green/ blue, a blue and a purple).
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a divided core in alternating swirls of flame/ green and flame/ white/ blue with outer groups of hair stripes in alternating flame and white.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a swirled orange latticino core and alternating blue and white stripes.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a swirled orange latticino core and alternating stripes in white and colours (a purple, a green and a blue).
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a swirled white latticino core and alternating red and orange stripes.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a swirled orange latticino core and alternating coloured blue and green stripes with white edges.
[marbles] Marble of greenish clear glass with a swirled white latticino core and red stripes.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a swirled orange latticino core and alternating blue and green stripes with white edges.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a swirled white latticino core and alternating orange and coloured stripes (a purple, a green and a blue).
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a swirled white latticino core and alternating red and coloured stripes  (a green, a purple and a blue).
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a swirled orange latticino core and alternating white and coloured stripes (a purple, a green and a blue).
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a swirled white latticino core and alternating flame and coloured stripes (a green and a blue).
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a swirled white latticino core and alternating flame and  coloured stripes (a green and a blue).
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a divided swirled core of white, green and blue with orange hair stripes.
[marbles] Marble of green glass with mica flecks suspended within it.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a divided swirled core of flame, green and orange with white hair stripes.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a divided swirled core of white, green, flame and blue with yellow hair stripes.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a divided swirled core of white, flame and blue.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a divided swirled core of white, orange and purple.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a divided swirled core of white, orange, green and blue, with hair stripes of orange.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a divided swirled core of white, flame, green and blue, with hair stripes of white and orange.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a divided swirled core of white, flame, green purple and blue, with hair stripes of orange.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a divided swirled core of white, flame, purple and blue, with hair stripes of yellow.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a divided swirled core of white, flame, green and blue, with hair stripes of white and orange.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a divided swirled core of white, flame, green and blue, with hair stripes of white and orange.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a swirled ribbon core of white, orange, flame, green and blue, and hair stripes of white and yellow.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a swirled ribbon core of white, flame and  green, and hair stripes of white and orange.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a swirled ribbon core of white, orange, green and blue.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a swirled hair stripe ribbon core of yellow, and outer stripes of white,  flame, and purple.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a swirled white striped core and alternating stripes of flame and blue.
[marbles] Marble of clear glass with a swirled white striped core and alternating stripes of flame and blue.
[sheets (information artifacts)] Pink paper sheet, printed in black with a diagram and instructions for playing the game of Solitaire on the obverse, and an advertisement for the same manufacturer's 'Tick-Tock' game (with a photogravure illustration) on the reverse.
[sheets (information artifacts)] Pale green paper sheet, printed in black with instructions for playing the game of 'German Tactics' on the obverse, and an advertisement for the same manufacturer's games 'Catelle' and Spinanspell' (with a photogravure illustration) on the reverse.
[Box] Squared brown cardboard box lid, stapled together at the corners.  In the centre of the lid is pasted a squared label of grey paper printed in dark blue with the words 'The Game of GERMAN TACTICS and SOLITAIRE/ Published by John Jaques & Son, Ltd., London' within a decorative border of stylized linear flowers and foliage.
[Box] Squared brown cardboard box, stapled together at the corners.
